	<h1 class="title">因为不够中立，扎克伯格的免费互联网在印度被叫停</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/73517/small/73517.jpg?1431406847" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">赖江锟 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-12-24 13:50:50 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/19655/medium/19655.jpg?1450933876" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


